      "solution": "import java.util.*;\nimport java.io.*;\nimport java.math.*;\nclass Solution {\n    public static char[][] tab;\n    public static int N,nbEtage;\n    public static void main(String args[]) {\n        Scanner in = new Scanner(System.in);\n        N = in.nextInt(); \n        maxTriangle();\n        int haut = nbEtage*4;\n        int larg = 6*nbEtage-1;\n        tab = new char[haut][larg];\n        init();\n        int x=haut-1;\n        for(int i=0;i<nbEtage;i++){\n            addGlasses(nbEtage-i,x-i*4,i*3);\n        }\n        afficher();\n    }\n    public static void init(){\n        for(int i=0;i<tab.length;i++){\n            for(int j=0;j<tab[i].length;j++){\n                tab[i][j]=' ';\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    public static void afficher(){\n        for(int i=0;i<tab.length;i++){\n            for(int j=0;j<tab[i].length;j++){\n                System.out.format(\"%1s\",tab[i][j]);\n            }\n            System.out.println(\"\");\n        }\n    }\n    public static void addGlasses(int nb, int ligne, int decal){\n        for(int i=0;i<nb;i++){\n            tab[ligne-0][1+decal+i*6]='*';\n            tab[ligne-0][3+decal+i*6]='*';\n            tab[ligne-0][0+decal+i*6]='*';\n            tab[ligne-0][2+decal+i*6]='*';\n            tab[ligne-0][4+decal+i*6]='*';\n            tab[ligne-3][2+decal+i*6]='*';\n            tab[ligne-1][1+decal+i*6]='*';\n            tab[ligne-1][3+decal+i*6]='*';\n            tab[ligne-2][1+decal+i*6]='*';\n            tab[ligne-2][3+decal+i*6]='*';\n            tab[ligne-1][2+decal+i*6]=' ';\n            tab[ligne-2][2+decal+i*6]=' ';\n            tab[ligne-3][1+decal+i*6]='*';\n            tab[ligne-3][3+decal+i*6]='*';\n        }\n    }\n    public static void maxTriangle(){\n        nbEtage=1;\n        for(int i=1;i<N;i++){\n            if ((i*(i+1))/2<=N){\n                nbEtage=i;\n            }\n        }\n        System.err.println(\"With \"+N+\" glasses, I can do a pyramid of \"+nbEtage+\" stage(s)\\n\");\n        System.err.println(\"Like this : \\n\");\n    }\n}",
      "statement": "You are given a number, [[N]], of glasses. Your job is to determine the largest pyramid that can be built with the glasses provided, and then create that pyramid in the output.\n\nA glass is represented in ASCII as follows:\n\n\n` ***    \n * *    \n * *    \n*****`",
